<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <meta name="Author" content="Takatty">
        <meta name="title" content="Sharechat">
        <title></title>
        <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/chat-text.css' />
        <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/responsive/chat-text-responsive.css'/>
    </head>

    <body>

        <header>
            <div class="header-title">
                <h1>Room Name</h1>
                <p>このページでは、チャットメッセージの編集や削除が選択出来ます。</p>
            </div>
        </header>

        <main>
            <div class="chat">
                <div class="chat-show">
                    <div class="chat-people">
                        <div class="chat-people-img">
                            <p>
                                <img src="/images/human.png" width="130" height="130">
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="chat-people-name">
                            <p><%= user.name %></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="chat-content">
                        <form action="" method="POST">
                            <div class="chat-mess">
                                <p>
                                    <input type="text" value='<%= text.text %>' name="text">
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="buttoms">
                                <p>
                                    <input type="button" value="<%= delete_bottom%>">
                                </p>
        
                                <p>
                                    <input type="submit" value="<%= edit_bottom %>" onClick="location.href='/chat/<%= text.room_id %>/text/<%= text.message_id %>/account/<%= text.user_id %>/edit'" class="account-bottom">
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>

        <footer>

        </footer>
      
    </body>

</html>
